Bulma主题模板
=============

基于`bulma.css`为Django开发提供常用的页面模板

Screenshots
-----------

.. figure:: ./login.jpeg
   :alt: Login Page

   Login Page

.. figure:: ./profile.jpeg
   :alt: User Profile

   User Profile

Quick Start
-----------

Install Package

.. code:: bash

   pip install django-bulmacss

修改`settings.py\`

.. code:: bash

   INSTALLED_APPS = [
       'bulma',
       ...
   ]

   FORM_RENDERER = 'django.forms.renderers.TemplatesSetting'

